text: Arhopaloscelis maculatus is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Bates in 1877. It is known from Japan and Taiwan.BioLib.cz - Arhopaloscelis maculatus. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1877
title: Arhopaloscelis maculatus
